              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "W1Cut",
                  "name": "specA1",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "(1) Hover intent：onMouseEnter 起 ~200ms 後才設 hover-intent 並觸發抓資料；mouse 在 200ms 內離開就不抓（onMouseLeave 清 timer）。視覺 hover（image scale-105 / play overlay / kebab）維持即時 — delay 只套在抓 detail。觸控不會觸發 onMouseEnter → 自然只顯示年份，符合預期。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "hgPfz",
                  "name": "specA2",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "(2) 資料：useQuery({ queryKey: ['tmdb', type, 'detail', id], queryFn: …, enabled: hoverIntent, staleTime: 24h（比照 project caching 設定）})。沿用 detail 頁已在用的端點 — 電影 GET /api/v1/tmdb/movies/:id → runtime；影集 GET /api/v1/tmdb/tv/:id → number_of_seasons / number_of_episodes。⚠️ Rule 15：DEV 先 grep apps/api/cmd/api/main.go 確認 route 已掛＋核對 handler 的 method+path（detail 頁有用 → 理應已掛；若沒 → 新增 task+AC 擴 scope，不要默默補）。資料只要在 TanStack 快取裡就顯示（即使是 detail 頁先載過的）— hover 只是把它載進來的觸發。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "q5hhUB",
                  "name": "specA3",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "(3) 文字組裝（zh-TW，建議抽純函數 formatRuntime / formatSeriesCount）：電影 runtime ≥ 60 → ${Math.floor(r/60)} 小時 ${r%60} 分，但 r%60===0 省略「0 分」→「2 小時」；runtime < 60 → ${r} 分鐘；runtime 為 0/null/undefined → extra 留空（只剩年份）。影集 seasons 與 episodes 都有 → ${seasons} 季 ${episodes} 集；只有 seasons → ${seasons} 季；都沒有 → extra 留空。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "MTdF6",
                  "name": "specA4",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "(4) 組合與排版：year 有 + extra 有 → ${year} · ${extra}；只有 year → ${year}；只有 extra（少見）→ ${extra}；都沒 → 不 render <p>（現狀）。維持單行 truncate、text-xs text-[var(--text-secondary)]、mt-2 區塊不變；資料到達後就地換字（可選給 <p> 加 transition-opacity duration-200 微淡入，非必要）。同一行字數變動不得推擠卡片版面。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Ihlnr",
                  "name": "specA5",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "(5) 高亮：title 仍走 <HighlightText query={highlightQuery} />；metadata 行不需高亮。檔案：apps/web/src/components/media/PosterCard.tsx（＋新 util，例如 apps/web/src/lib/formatMedia.ts，附 formatMedia.spec.ts）。",
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
