              "content": "• Rule 21：PosterCard.tsx 檔頭目前是 // Implements: Component/PosterCardHover (MQbvp)；本故事同時動到預設態（RusTY 的下方文字）→ DEV 更新為 // Implements: Component/PosterCard (RusTY) + Component/PosterCardHover (MQbvp)",
